public class XSLTpro2004Crosswalk
extends XSLTCrosswalk

Convert native "item" to pro. In this case, the native "item" is assumed to already be formatted as an OAI element, with the possible exception that multiple metadataFormats may be present in the element. The "crosswalk", merely involves pulling out the one that is requested.
